<Layout::Text text-l text-f>
	<Docs::Heading @level="3">Example usage</Docs::Heading>
	<p>To display the current command-line tool version, along with the platform and architecture, in a terminal run the <Ascua::Prism::Inline @language="shell" @code="surreal version" /> command without any further arguments.</p>
	<codes vertical>
		<Code @name="docs-cli-isready-main.shell" text="Command line">
			user@localhost % surreal isready --conn http://localhost:8000
		</Code>
		<pre class="language-txt"><code class="language-txt">OK</code></pre>
	</codes>
